caption: #contest     I'm not The type of person who writes a big text.? But I would really like to meet you jack's. I love your songs, especially your new songs "California" and "how we living". I think both songs  have a message.            And every time I see a picture of a fan who had met you I wish that this was me. I hope that soon I will be that girl on a picture with you.❤️ I'm from Germany and that's why my English is so bad, but I hope that you understood me. I don't think that I will win this contest, but I still have little bit of hope. AND it would be pretty great if you guys come to Germany because my friend and me would really like to be on a concert from you.:) Yeah, that's it.?? #jackandjack #jackjohnson #jackgilinksy #selfie
